messages.messageBody:
Hi,

My name is Laura and my husband is Brian.
We have four wonderful kids ages 12, 4.5, 2 and 3 months.
Our family lives in Maine near the NH line.
I have been here for a couple weeks but just have not had the time to do an
intro. I am also on the Discussion list which is how I found this list. I know
Im one of a few Laura's on a couple lists so I will locate a sig line or
something that identifies me.

I also booked my room for Peabody the other day im so excited! Love the
topics they have been great reads especially the grabbing toys and sib trouble
which we are seeing the past several weeks.
Laura
for now-from Maine
